.meas tran v12_b7 FIND v(d7) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=12
.meas tran v12_b6 FIND v(d6) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=12
.meas tran v12_b5 FIND v(d5) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=12
.meas tran v12_b4 FIND v(d4) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=12
