.meas tran v12_b0 FIND v(d0) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=12

.meas tran v13_b7 FIND v(d7) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=13
.meas tran v13_b6 FIND v(d6) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=13
.meas tran v13_b5 FIND v(d5) WHEN v(valid)=0.9 RISE=13
